metadata.name: Calypso #1/3
metadata.description:
On a mindful pause for a moment of serene stillness, the Calypso earring rests in a Zen garden, emanating a positive vibrational frequency from a freshwater pearl.

Center of Calm artworks include:

1. digital art — ERC-721 NFT.

2. Physical jewelry — pair of earrings in gold vermeil with freshwater pearls, handmade in Toronto, Canada.

3. Printed card of authenticity.
